metadata.name: Selma the Night Witch
metadata.description:
-Selma was once an insane witch who, one day, looked up at the stars and discovered many of its hidden secrets on her own. 

- No one knows what goes on in her head, but one thing is for certain is that she does not adhere to any Coven. She believes they are a waste of time.

-Encountering Selma is often considered bad luck, as she is well know for pulling off ridiculous pranks as she roams between different realms for sheer amusement.
